# Hosts we don't want to pester on every CI run (rate limiting, flaky
# status codes). Each line is a regex matched against the full URL.

# GitHub throttles the link-checker by IP. Pin to public repo URLs
# and accept that; the release URL is stable.
^https://github\.com/.*/releases$

# Example/placeholder hosts used in docs — intentionally non-resolving.
^https?://dgp\.example\.com
^https?://your-objectstorage\.com
^https?://s3\.example\.com
